    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main goal of this French multicenter observational cohort study is to prospectively
      collect data assessing the impact of the Adaptative Servo-Ventilation treatment on the
      quality of sleep of patients with central or combined sleep apnea syndrome (SAS) out of Heart
      Failure (HF) with altered ejection fraction, with a predominant central SAS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
